'''Cinemateca Nacional del Ecuador''' is a [[film archive]] located in [[Ecuador]]. It was established in 1981 and the collection comprises 4000 films and 10,000 documents.<ref>[http://www.cinematecaecuador.com/Home/About About]</ref>
