'''''The Pennsylvania Manual''''' is a biennial guide to the [[Government of Pennsylvania]] produced by the [[Pennsylvania Department of General Services]].<ref name=DGS>{{Cite web |title=The Pennsylvania Manual |work=Publications |publisher=Pennsylvania Department of General Services |url=http://www.dgs.pa.gov/State%20Government/Print,%20Design%20and%20Mail%20Services/Pages/The-Pennsylvania-Manual.aspx}}</ref> The ''Pennsylvania Manual'' has been published by the Pennsylvania Government for over 200&nbsp;years.<ref name=DGS /> In 2016, the 122nd volume was printed.

